He announces the birth of his own son to shepherds.

80
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:29,910
Now, shepherding was actually the first profession named in the Bible.

81
00:06:30,790 --> 00:06:35,010
And throughout the history of Israel, it was a respectable calling.

82
00:06:35,010 --> 00:06:41,870
But by the time we get to Jesus' time, shepherding had fallen out of respect.

83
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:51,080
Shepherding had become seen as a class of wild people, unclean peasants, if you will.

84
