And let's be honest, being a shepherd was lonely, wearisome, often boring, tedious, sometimes dangerous.

85
00:07:01,550 --> 00:07:06,750
Gave them a lot of contact with sheep, not a lot of exposure to people.

86
00:07:07,970 --> 00:07:13,810
So you can imagine their manners deteriorating as they work hard at this profession.

87
00:07:15,060 --> 00:07:16,640
They had lots of time on their hands.

88
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:22,340
That's why many of them learned to play instruments, sit out in the field and play the flute or the harp or something like that.

89
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:26,340
Lots of time to kill, not a lot of time with people.

90
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:28,220
Let's be honest.

91
