They didn't have a nine-to-five job, two kids, two car garage, fence with a swing in the backyard.

94
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:48,270
No, these were wanderers, drifters, even characterized by some as thieves.

95
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,880
You can't trust the shepherds.

96
