As the scriptures say, the person who wishes to boast should boast only of what the Lord has done.

129
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:41,600
God gave the message to the lowest.

130
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:42,180
Why?

131
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:45,860
