I sat Eric in a high chair and noticed everyone was quietly eating and talking.

148
00:11:04,450 --> 00:11:08,130
And suddenly Eric squealed with glee and he said,

149
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:09,050
Hi there!

150
00:11:09,930 --> 00:11:15,550
And he wiggled and he giggled with merriment at a man with a tattered rag of a coat

151
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:18,230
and dirty and greasy and worn.

152
00:11:19,250 --> 00:11:21,950
His pants were baggy with a zipper at half-mast,

153
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:24,670
and his toes poked out of the would-be shoes.

154
00:11:25,730 --> 00:11:30,190
His shirt was dirty, and his hair was uncombed and unwashed.

155
00:11:31,170 --> 00:11:33,070
His whiskers were not quite a beard,

156
00:11:33,070 --> 00:11:37,710
and varicose charted a complex map across his nose.

157
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:43,620
We were too far to smell him, but I'm sure he smelled.

158
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:46,390
His hands waved at my baby.

159
00:11:46,770 --> 00:11:48,790
Hi there, baby. Hi there, big boy.

160
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:50,430
I see you, buster.

161
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:56,060
The man said to Eric, and my husband and I didn't know what to do.

162
00:11:57,100 --> 00:12:00,940
And Eric continued to laugh and answer, hi, hi there.

163
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:07,790
Well, our meal finally came, and the drunken geezer began shouting across the room, hey,

164
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:09,030
do you know patty cake?

165
00:12:09,410 --> 00:12:10,610
Do you know peekaboo?

166
00:12:10,970 --> 00:12:12,650
Hey, look, he knows peekaboo.

167
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:15,360
No one thought the man was cute.

168
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:20,800
My husband and I were embarrassed and Eric, on the other hand, was just running through

169
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:24,860
his repertoire of tricks and all admired by this gentleman.

170
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,620
We finally got through the meal.

171
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:35,080
My husband went to pay and Eric and I headed for the door, but the old man was poised between

172
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,340
